@startuml diagrama-sequencia
' Diagrama de sequencia do laco de animacao do AlgorithmVision.
' Renderize com PlantUML: plantuml diagrama-sequencia.puml (gera PNG)
title Laco de animacao (Swing Timer ~60 qps, tudo na EDT)

participant "Timer (16 ms)" as Timer
participant "JanelaPrincipal" as Janela
participant "PainelRenderizacao" as Painel
participant "ControladorSimulacao\n(ControladorMotorNativo)" as Ctrl
participant "MotorGrafico\n(JNI)" as Motor
participant "motor nativo\n(C++/OpenGL)" as Nativo

Timer -> Janela : actionPerformed()

Janela -> Ctrl : avancarSeNecessario()
alt intervalo (s/passo) decorrido
  Ctrl -> Motor : step()
  Motor -> Nativo : Java_main_MotorGrafico_step
  Nativo -> Nativo : SortEngine::step()\n(um passo do algoritmo)
end

Janela -> Painel : atualizarQuadro()
Painel -> Ctrl : renderizar(largura, altura, pixels)
Ctrl -> Motor : renderFrame(largura, altura, pixels)
Motor -> Nativo : Java_main_MotorGrafico_renderFrame
Nativo -> Nativo : desenha no FBO offscreen\n(SortRenderer + shaders)
Nativo -> Nativo : glReadPixels + conversao\nRGBA -> ARGB + flip vertical
Nativo --> Motor : true (pixels preenchidos)
Motor --> Ctrl : true
Ctrl --> Painel : true
Painel -> Painel : repaint()\n(paintComponent desenha a BufferedImage)

Janela -> Ctrl : obterStatus() / obterComparacoes() / obterAcessos()
Ctrl --> Janela : metricas exibidas no PainelControles

note over Timer, Nativo
  Contrato de thread unica: init(), step(), renderFrame() e cleanup()
  sao todos chamados na Event Dispatch Thread, dona do contexto OpenGL.
end note
@enduml
